  "texts": [
    "The key ingredients are (i) a compact physical model whose number of parameters does not depend on the environment's complexity and that does not require an explicit description of the unknown environment, and (ii) the estimation of the physical model's parameters.",
    "Compared to deep-learning benchmarks, our physical model offers orders-of-magnitude improvements in terms of compactness (the number of model parameters), accuracy, and the number of required calibration examples.",
    "Moreover, our approach enjoys a favorable scaling of the number of required calibration examples with the number of considered scattering coefficients.",
    "Strikingly, we discover that natural constraints built into the physical model enable the complete and accurate estimation of its parameters without every measuring phase, or without ever measuring some of the considered scattering coefficients.",
    "Thereby, we unlock previously unimagined frugal wave-control paradigms."
  ],
